title: Lumberjanes 001 - 018
description: This is a simple compilation of the "Lumberjanes" series so far, Issues 001-018. I removed some minor details in a couple of file names ("2Covers" mostly)and harmonized the way the files were labeled in the original scans, to make it more ocd-friendly. That said, i did not upload the single files myself and hereby wish to thank those who did. Hope you enjoy it as much as i did, and if you do too, dear leechers, you surely will reseed generously and maybe even go to a store and buy the original print version
